abla_{W^{(k)}} =  egin{bmatrix} \delta_{1}^{(k+1)}a_{1}^{(k)} & \delta_{1}^{(k+1)}a_{2}^{(k)} & \cdots \ \delta_{2}^{(k+1)}a_{1}^{(k)} & \delta_{2}^{(k+1)}a_{2}^{(k)} & \cdots \ \vdots & \vdots & \ddots \ \end{bmatrix} = \delta^{(k+1)}a^{(k)T} \ 
